{"tid":2064943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩女生被指新城市廣場塗鴉扶手電梯  2中五女生被控刑毀准保釋","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:30:19.000Z","uid":10540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6efafa6802461b5554fd52acc3e410d3c99df8d2","tid":2064943,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:18:30.000Z","msg":"反修例風波踏入一周年，多區有零星衝突，兩名中五女學生涉嫌塗鴉沙田新城市廣場的扶手電梯，被控刑事損壞罪，案件今在沙田裁判法院提堂。裁判官應辯方要求，押後案件至8月10日，另質疑控方提出的保釋條件過於嚴苛，衡量過控罪嚴重性及被告人身自由後，下令兩被告保釋期間不得離港、每周向警署報到及遵守宵禁令，但不必禁足。<br />\n<br />\n被告同被控於上周五，損壞沙田新城市廣場L3至L2的扶手電梯。黃另被控於同日同地損壞L2至L1的扶手電梯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1796245/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B6%89%E5%A1%97%E9%B4%89%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E6%89%B6%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%BB%E6%A2%AF-2%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1796245%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25A1%2597%25E9%25B4%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2589%25B6%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A2%25AF-2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8kpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=3aafac68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1796245%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25A1%2597%25E9%25B4%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2589%25B6%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25A2%25AF-2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%2587%2586